{"ja506:0.1":"Jataka ","ja506:0.2":"Visatinipata ","ja506:0.3":"Matangavagga ","ja506:0.4":"10. Campeyyajataka ","ja506:1.1":"“Ka nu vijjurivabhasi, ","ja506:1.2":"Osadhi viya taraka; ","ja506:1.3":"Devata nusi gandhabbi, ","ja506:1.4":"Na tam mannami manusim”. ","ja506:2.1":"“Namhi devi na gandhabbi, ","ja506:2.2":"na maharaja manusi; ","ja506:2.3":"Nagakannasmi bhaddante, ","ja506:2.4":"atthenamhi idhagata”. ","ja506:3.1":"“Vibbhantacitta kupitindriyasi, ","ja506:3.2":"Nettehi te varigana savanti; ","ja506:3.3":"Kim te nattham kim pana patthayana, ","ja506:3.4":"Idhagata nari tadingha bruhi”. ","ja506:4.1":"“Yamuggatejo uragoti cahu, ","ja506:4.2":"Nagoti nam ahu jana janinda; ","ja506:4.3":"Tamaggahi puriso jivikattho, ","ja506:4.4":"Tam bandhana munca pati mameso”. ","ja506:5.1":"“Katham nvayam balaviriyupapanno, ","ja506:5.2":"Hatthattamagacchi vanibbakassa; ","ja506:5.3":"Akkhahi me nagakanne tamattham, ","ja506:5.4":"Katham vijanemu gahitanagam”. ","ja506:6.1":"“Nagarampi nago bhasmam kareyya, ","ja506:6.2":"Tatha hi so balaviriyupapanno; ","ja506:6.3":"Dhammanca nago apacayamano, ","ja506:6.4":"Tasma parakkamma tapo karoti. ","ja506:7.1":"Catuddasim pancadasinca raja, ","ja506:7.2":"Catuppathe sammati nagaraja; ","ja506:7.3":"Tamaggahi puriso jivikattho, ","ja506:7.4":"Tam bandhana munca pati mameso”. ","ja506:8.1":"“Solasitthisahassani, ","ja506:8.2":"amuttamanikundala; ","ja506:8.3":"Varigehasaya nari, ","ja506:8.4":"tapi tam saranam gata. ","ja506:9.1":"Dhammena mocehi asahasena, ","ja506:9.2":"Gamena nikkhena gavam satena; ","ja506:9.3":"Ossatthakayo urago caratu, ","ja506:9.4":"Punnatthiko muncatu bandhanasma”. ","ja506:10.1":"“Dhammena mocemi asahasena, ","ja506:10.2":"Gamena nikkhena gavam satena; ","ja506:10.3":"Ossatthakayo urago caratu, ","ja506:10.4":"Punnatthiko muncatu bandhanasma. ","ja506:11.1":"Dammi nikkhasatam ludda, ","ja506:11.2":"thulanca manikundalam; ","ja506:11.3":"Catussadanca pallankam, ","ja506:11.4":"umapupphasarinnibham. ","ja506:12.1":"Dve ca sadisiyo bhariya, ","ja506:12.2":"Usabhanca gavam satam; ","ja506:12.3":"Ossatthakayo urago caratu, ","ja506:12.4":"Punnatthiko muncatu bandhanasma”. ","ja506:13.1":"“Vinapi dana tava vacanam janinda, ","ja506:13.2":"Muncemu nam uragam bandhanasma; ","ja506:13.3":"Ossatthakayo urago caratu, ","ja506:13.4":"Punnatthiko muncatu bandhanasma”. ","ja506:14.1":"Mutto campeyyako nago, ","ja506:14.2":"rajanam etadabravi; ","ja506:14.3":"“Namo te kasirajatthu, ","ja506:14.4":"namo te kasivaddhana; ","ja506:14.5":"Anjalim te pagganhami, ","ja506:14.6":"passeyyam me nivesanam”. ","ja506:15.1":"“Addha hi dubbissasametamahu, ","ja506:15.2":"Yam manuso vissase amanusamhi; ","ja506:15.3":"Sace ca mam yacasi etamattham, ","ja506:15.4":"Dakkhemu te naga nivesanani”. ","ja506:16.1":"“Sacepi vato girimavaheyya, ","ja506:16.2":"Cando ca suriyo ca chama pateyyum; ","ja506:16.3":"Sabba ca najjo patisotam vajeyyum, ","ja506:16.4":"Na tvevaham raja musa bhaneyyam. ","ja506:17.1":"Nabham phaleyya udadhipi susse, ","ja506:17.2":"Samvattaye bhutadhara vasundhara; ","ja506:17.3":"Siluccayo meru samulamuppate, ","ja506:17.4":"Na tvevaham raja musa bhaneyyam”. ","ja506:18.1":"“Addha hi dubbissasametamahu, ","ja506:18.2":"Yam manuso vissase amanusamhi; ","ja506:18.3":"Sace ca mam yacasi etamattham, ","ja506:18.4":"Dakkhemu te naga nivesanani. ","ja506:19.1":"Tumhe khottha ghoravisa ulara, ","ja506:19.2":"Mahateja khippakopi ca hotha; ","ja506:19.3":"Mankarana bandhanasma pamutto, ","ja506:19.4":"Arahasi no janituye katani”. ","ja506:20.1":"“So paccatam niraye ghorarupe, ","ja506:20.2":"Ma kayikam satamalattha kinci; ","ja506:20.3":"Pelaya baddho maranam upetu, ","ja506:20.4":"Yo tadisam kammakatam na jane”. ","ja506:21.1":"“Saccappatinna tava mesa hotu, ","ja506:21.2":"Akkodhano hohi anupanahi; ","ja506:21.3":"Sabbanca te nagakulam supanna, ","ja506:21.4":"Aggimva gimhesu vivajjayantu”. ","ja506:22.1":"“Anukampasi nagakulam janinda, ","ja506:22.2":"Mata yatha suppiyam ekaputtam; ","ja506:22.3":"Ahanca te nagakulena saddhim, ","ja506:22.4":"Kahami veyyavatikam ularam”. ","ja506:23.1":"“Yojentu ve rajarathe sucitte, ","ja506:23.2":"Kambojake assatare sudante; ","ja506:23.3":"Nage ca yojentu suvannakappane, ","ja506:23.4":"Dakkhemu nagassa nivesanani”. ","ja506:24.1":"Bheri mudinga panava ca sankha, ","ja506:24.2":"Avajjayimsu uggasenassa ranno; ","ja506:24.3":"Payasi raja bahusobhamano, ","ja506:24.4":"Purakkhato nariganassa majjhe. ","ja506:25.1":"Suvannacitakam bhumim, ","ja506:25.2":"addakkhi kasivaddhano; ","ja506:25.3":"Sovannamayapasade, ","ja506:25.4":"veluriyaphalakatthate. ","ja506:26.1":"Sa raja pavisi byamham, ","ja506:26.2":"campeyyassa nivesanam; ","ja506:26.3":"Adiccavannasannibham, ","ja506:26.4":"kamsavijju pabhassaram. ","ja506:27.1":"Nanarukkhehi sanchannam, ","ja506:27.2":"nanagandhasamiritam; ","ja506:27.3":"So pavekkhi kasiraja, ","ja506:27.4":"campeyyassa nivesanam. ","ja506:28.1":"Pavitthasmim kasiranne, ","ja506:28.2":"campeyyassa nivesanam; ","ja506:28.3":"Dibba turiya pavajjimsu, ","ja506:28.4":"nagakanna ca naccisum. ","ja506:29.1":"Tam nagakanna caritam ganena, ","ja506:29.2":"Anvaruhi kasiraja pasanno; ","ja506:29.3":"Nisidi sovannamayamhi pithe, ","ja506:29.4":"Sapassaye candanasaralitte. ","ja506:30.1":"So tattha bhutva ca atho ramitva, ","ja506:30.2":"Campeyyakam kasiraja avoca; ","ja506:30.3":"“Vimanasetthani imani tuyham, ","ja506:30.4":"Adiccavannani pabhassarani; ","ja506:30.5":"Netadisam atthi manussaloke, ","ja506:30.6":"Kim patthayam naga tapo karosi. ","ja506:31.1":"Ta kambukayuradhara suvattha, ","ja506:31.2":"Vattanguli tambatalupapanna; ","ja506:31.3":"Paggayha payenti anomavanna, ","ja506:31.4":"Netadisam atthi manussaloke; ","ja506:31.5":"Kim patthayam naga tapo karosi. ","ja506:32.1":"Najjo ca tema puthulomamaccha, ","ja506:32.2":"Ata sakuntabhiruda sutittha; ","ja506:32.3":"Netadisam atthi manussaloke, ","ja506:32.4":"Kim patthayam naga tapo karosi. ","ja506:33.1":"Konca mayura diviya ca hamsa, ","ja506:33.2":"Vaggussara kokila sampatanti; ","ja506:33.3":"Netadisam atthi manussaloke, ","ja506:33.4":"Kim patthayam naga tapo karosi. ","ja506:34.1":"Amba ca sala tilaka ca jambuyo, ","ja506:34.2":"Uddalaka pataliyo ca phulla; ","ja506:34.3":"Netadisam atthi manussaloke, ","ja506:34.4":"Kim patthayam naga tapo karosi. ","ja506:35.1":"Ima ca te pokkharanno samantato, ","ja506:35.2":"Dibba ca gandha satatam pavayanti; ","ja506:35.3":"Netadisam atthi manussaloke, ","ja506:35.4":"Kim patthayam naga tapo karosi”. ","ja506:36.1":"“Na puttahetu na dhanassa hetu, ","ja506:36.2":"Na ayuno capi janinda hetu; ","ja506:36.3":"Manussayonim abhipatthayano, ","ja506:36.4":"Tasma parakkamma tapo karomi”. ","ja506:37.1":"“Tvam lohitakkho vihatantaramso, ","ja506:37.2":"Alankato kappitakesamassu; ","ja506:37.3":"Surosito lohitacandanena, ","ja506:37.4":"Gandhabbarajava disa pabhasasi. ","ja506:38.1":"Deviddhipattosi mahanubhavo, ","ja506:38.2":"Sabbehi kamehi samangibhuto; ","ja506:38.3":"Pucchami tam nagarajetamattham, ","ja506:38.4":"Seyyo ito kena manussaloko”. ","ja506:39.1":"“Janinda nannatra manussaloka, ","ja506:39.2":"Suddhi va samvijjati samyamo va; ","ja506:39.3":"Ahanca laddhana manussayonim, ","ja506:39.4":"Kahami jatimaranassa antam”. ","ja506:40.1":"“Addha have sevitabba sapanna, ","ja506:40.2":"Bahussuta ye bahuthanacintino; ","ja506:40.3":"Nariyo ca disvana tuvanca naga, ","ja506:40.4":"Kahami punnani anappakani”. ","ja506:41.1":"“Addha have sevitabba sapanna, ","ja506:41.2":"Bahussuta ye bahuthanacintino; ","ja506:41.3":"Nariyo ca disvana mamanca raja, ","ja506:41.4":"Karohi punnani anappakani”. ","ja506:42.1":"“Idanca me jatarupam pahutam, ","ja506:42.2":"Rasi suvannassa ca talamatta; ","ja506:42.3":"Ito haritvana suvannagharani, ","ja506:42.4":"Karassu rupiyapakaram karontu. ","ja506:43.1":"Mutta ca vahasahassani panca, ","ja506:43.2":"Veluriyamissani ito haritva; ","ja506:43.3":"Antepure bhumiyam santharantu, ","ja506:43.4":"Nikkaddama hehiti niraja ca. ","ja506:44.1":"Etadisam avasa rajasettha, ","ja506:44.2":"Vimanasettham bahu sobhamanam; ","ja506:44.3":"Baranasim nagaram iddham phitam, ","ja506:44.4":"Rajjanca karehi anomapanna”ti. ","ja506:45.1":"Campeyyajatakam dasamam. "}